-- Paul McGinley Named European Captain for Golf’s Ryder Cup
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2013-01-15T18:19:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-15/paul-mcginley-named-european-captain-for-golf-s-ryder-cup.html
Ireland’s Paul McGinley was named
captain of the European squad for golf’s Ryder Cup for the 2014
competition at Gleneagles, Scotland.  The 46-year-old was a vice captain for the team at the 2010
event at Celtic Manor Resort in Newport,  Wales . He was
introduced by the European Tour at a press conference today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  